service.tut.pori.facebookjazz

Class FacebookPhotoTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.facebookjazz.FacebookPhotoTag

  • public class FacebookPhotoTag
extends java.lang.Object
    Tag of a photo retrieved from Facebook.

    Optional Elements

    • serviceId. Not present if the tag was created by the user or internally by the service.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<photoTag>
  <serviceId>4</serviceId>
  <value>PrOkZMZWXENOXWfdgGCJsPiYjZlFVpxkSbopyLHikvKzhUUDIHFNSSTiYhYmqrBr</value>
</photoTag>
